      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Grid Convergence Index Study — Hemolysis QoI",
      "description": "Three systematically refined meshes (coarse 1.8 M cells, medium 5.4 M cells, fine 16.2 M cells) were used to compute GCI per Roache 1994. Observed order of accuracy p = 1.97; GCI_fine = 1.3 %.",
      "comparedAgainst": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/morrison-cfd-mesh-convergence-study",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/morrison-gci-computation-run"
    },
